Requirements and notes
- you also need the Xcite! Partner script to make this run
- so you have to be a Xcite! Partner
- I will not offer support to non Xcite! Partners
- I may change the API at any time, so don't expect any backward compatibility
- If you are using this you should consider to give something back to the community

